videoSnippet.title: Take The Knight, Penguin! | Carlsen vs Tang | Lichess Titled Arena
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Hello everyone!
Today my channel hit 100000 subscribers! 
Thank you all for your constant support and for sharing your love for chess with the world. Words fail to describe this joy :) 
Now that I've reached this milestone, it's time to continue doing what I enjoy doing most... some more chess videos for you guys :)
You will hear from me soon with some information about my 100k Subscribers stream, giveaways, Lichess tournament with prizes and more. See you soon :)

Magnus Carlsen vs Andrew Tang
Lichess Titled Arena (2018) 
Queen's Gambit Declined: Tartakower Defense (D58)

1. d4 d5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. c4 e6 4. Nc3 Be7 5. Bg5 h6 6. Bh4 O-O 7. e3 b6 8. g4 dxc4 9. Rg1 Nd5 10. Bxe7 Qxe7 11. g5 h5 12. Ne5 g6 13. Bxc4 Bb7 14. Qc2 Nd7 15. Nxg6 fxg6 16. Qxg6+ Kh8 17. Bd3 Qf7 18. Qh6+ Kg8 19. O-O-O Rae8 20. Ne4 Qg7 21. Nf6+ Kf7 22. g6+ Kxf6 23. Qg5#
